snippet.description:
The day we did the final burnout for a Daily Transmission episode at the Donut Garage was a sad, sad day. How can you do hoodrat things with your friends, when the city shuts you down?? So we searched far and wide for a new home and now, finally, we’ve got it. An all new studio. In Compton, CA. Follow us on the journey of building out this brand new spot: AKA Tire Slayer Studios. 

 WE CAN SHRED AGAIN. IT’S A BEAUTIFUL THING.


We’ve got channels for all your car content needs. Subscribe, nerds.

The Hoonigans: https://www.youtube.com/user/TheHoonigans?sub_confirmation=1

